request.description:
Get payment request details by reference.

Response shape:
- reference, amount, status, from_date, to_date, requested_at, approved_at, paid_at, total_items
- breakdown: { base_earnings, penalties_deducted, coordinator_incentive, ops_adjustments }
- transaction_history[]: { event, label, timestamp, by, remarks }
- daily_breakdown: paginated by day
  { data: [{ date, count, day_total, deliveries[] }], meta: { current_page, per_page, total_days, last_page } }

Note: top-level deliveries[] has been removed — use daily_breakdown.data[].deliveries instead.

